Detailed Description

Struct to hold info about the file format for mesh.

Description:

Holds information pertinent to file IO for a mesh.

NOTE: purposefully do not have any dynamically allocated bits in here or we have to have a special free call (see _FC_DsFileIOInfo).

Modifications:

  • 7/18/2005 WSD created.

Field Documentation

int _FC_MeshFileIOInfo::id

Since some file formats use an abitrary number instead of name to specify a mesh, this field is used carry that ID along in case of writing to such formats (to keep ID consistent if rewriting to such a format). Should be 1 or greater.
